265
00:27:22,802 --> 00:27:24,596
for about six weeks while my brow grew back.

266
00:27:24,638 --> 00:27:25,472
Very embarrassing.

267
00:27:25,472 --> 00:27:27,557
You didn't take it again after that?

268
00:27:27,682 --> 00:27:28,767
Kenny, have you been listening to me?

269
00:27:28,767 --> 00:27:30,852
I shaved off my eyebrow.

270
00:27:31,228 --> 00:27:32,854
I wanted an experience Mr. Potter,

271
00:27:32,854 --> 00:27:34,564
not a career on stage.

272
00:27:38,318 --> 00:27:40,779
If you ever want to get high sir, I usually have some dope.

273
00:27:41,613 --> 00:27:43,824
You're really mad aren't you?

274
00:27:50,831 --> 00:27:51,498
I'm sorry, sir.

275
00:27:51,498 --> 00:27:54,125
I guess you don't feel very comfortable talking like this.

276
00:27:54,125 --> 00:27:55,460
What makes you say that?

277
00:27:55,460 --> 00:27:59,089
Lois thinks you're kind of cagey. Like this morning...

278
00:27:59,089 --> 00:27:59,965
...when you were listening to

279
00:27:59,965 --> 00:28:02,217
all that crap we were talking about Huxley.

280
00:28:02,259 --> 00:28:03,593
Well, not all of you.

281
00:28:03,593 --> 00:28:05,512
