286
00:28:16,523 --> 00:28:19,693
Well, maybe that's true up to a point.

287
00:28:21,111 --> 00:28:22,863
It's not that I want to be cagey.

288
00:28:24,030 --> 00:28:28,118
It's just that I can't really discuss things completely openly...

289
00:28:28,118 --> 00:28:28,869
...at school.

290
00:28:30,036 --> 00:28:31,580
Someone would misunderstand.

291
00:28:33,540 --> 00:28:36,168
I tried that today. It didn't really work out.

292
00:28:43,258 --> 00:28:44,968
