340
00:33:37,636 --> 00:33:39,012
They may be right.

341
00:33:41,014 --> 00:33:42,974
It will have to be another time. I'm late.

342
00:33:45,060 --> 00:33:46,686
But thank you for the invitation.

343
00:33:47,854 --> 00:33:49,523
And thank you for the talk earlier.

344
00:33:51,358 --> 00:33:52,901
And stay away from the mescaline.

345
00:34:26,393 --> 00:34:27,811
Hello, Mr. Falconer.

346
00:34:27,811 --> 00:34:30,063
Hello. How are you today?        I'm fine, sir.

347
00:34:30,063 --> 00:34:32,482
Do you need to get into your box?        Yes, I do.

348
00:34:32,983 --> 00:34:33,733
Follow me.

349
00:34:42,826 --> 00:34:43,910
Here you are, sir.

350
00:34:46,454 --> 00:34:48,081
If you could please sign here...

351
00:34:57,215 --> 00:34:58,175
Thank you.        Thank you.

352
00:36:06,326 --> 00:36:08,286
